  "texts": [
    "In Section 5 we obtain all of the relevant non-regularity results and in particular the proof of Proposition 1.5 and Theorem 1.4.",
    "The combination of these results is used to assert that Conjecture 1.1 fails.",
    "In Section 6 we develop some basic theory of flat chains and use it to obtain a proof of Theorem 1.7.",
    "The very short Section 7 is dedicated to obtaining a Lipschitz non-regularity result for the prescribed exterior derivative equation.",
    "AcknowledgementsI would like to express my gratitude to David Bate for bringing the Flat Chain Conjecture to my attention and for many fruitful discussions and careful reading of the manuscript."
